params.userPromptTemplate:
任务目标：{{goal}}
输出数量：{{count}}
来源列表(JSON)：{{sources}}

工作步骤要求：
1) 调用 dailyhot.fetch_topics，baseUrl 固定使用 https://dailyhotapi-hazel.vercel.app，perSourceLimit 设为 20
2) 仅基于返回 candidates 做语义筛选，优先满足任务目标关键词；若目标要求某主题（如学生/美国/日本），selected 必须与主题强相关
3) 如果强相关候选不足，允许返回少于 count，并在 discarded/summary 说明原因
4) 最后输出 {"action":"final","output":...}

final.output 结构必须为：{"selected":[{"rank":1,"title":"","source":"","sourceName":"","score":0-100,"reason":"","expected":{"exposure":0,"plays":0,"fans":0},"url":""}],"summary":"","discarded":[{"title":"","reason":""}]}
并且 selected 必须按优先级排序。
